hy kbIr! jo mnu`K r`b nwloN tu`tw hoieAw hY (jo 'dunIAw' dI ^wqr 'dIn' nUM gvweI jw irhw hY) aus nUM ieauN smJo ijvyN Qom dI BrI hoeI koTVI hY[
