hy kbIr! ('dIn' ivswr ky, prmwqmw nUM Bulw ky qUM jo puqR iesqRI Dn imlK Awidk) keI imqR bxw irhw hYN, ies mnu`Kw jnm ivc (iehnW imqRW qoN) suK nhIN imlygw[
